User Roles and Privileges:
-- Create a user with limited privileges
CREATE USER 'bookstore_user'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';
GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE ON BookstoreDB.* TO 'bookstore_user'@'localhost';


Data Encryption:
Ensure sensitive data is encrypted at rest and in transit.
-- Example: Encrypt email addresses using MySQL's built-in functions
UPDATE Customers SET Email = AES_ENCRYPT(Email, 'encryption_key');
